{"tid":1113287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拍片教男人如何打老婆　卡達學者：「調教妻子」家庭才會好","createTime":"2019-04-17T23:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T03:30:44.000Z","uid":122,"like":89,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"88b85e11ffc0b565414e663276c7bc3ea48372dd","tid":1113287,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T23:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190418/640_507b573e35db45ac32d988cf4ea85fb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190418%2F640_507b573e35db45ac32d988cf4ea85fb6.jpg&h=b2f885bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡達一名社會學家近日拍片，親自指導男性同胞，如何根據伊斯蘭教規「打老婆」，來展示「老公的地位與力量」。不過，他指，伊斯蘭教非常仁慈，禁止打臉，打老婆必須放輕力道。<br />\n<br />\n安薩里（Abad Al-Aziz Al-Khazraj Al-Ansari）上月29日在影音平台《YouTube》上，分享一段影片，教導穆斯林男性，如何打老婆，才能符合伊斯蘭教的懲罰方法。他表示，根據教規，「掌摑、揍頭，及打鼻子」都是不被允許的。而從他與另一男孩的示範可見，只能輕拍老婆的手臂，他說：「這樣打，就不會造成挫傷或流血」。<br />\n<br />\n安薩里強調，男人不一定非得打老婆，但男人是家中的領導人，要「調教」好妻子，家庭才會好，且女人的天性，喜歡暴力、強勢的老公。他提醒：「只有當老婆屢勸不聽，才可以用打人這最後手段。」最後，他聲稱，從未傷害過老婆。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190418/1552458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190418%2F1552458&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=858cf0bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190418%2F1552458&h=7d94d133\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190418/1552458</a><br />\n<br />\n老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2054adab4138cb48b7d581247b15f5d77b88ff7","tid":1113287,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T23:06:40.000Z","msg":"拍手臂叫打、食屎啦<br />\n利申、